description: The video shows a digital illustration of a yellow duckie with a shocked or fearful expression against a white background. The emoji is round and primarily yellow, fading to blue at the top. It has large, round white eyes with black pupils. Its mouth is wide open, revealing a dark red interior, and is outlined with a lighter orange color. Small, stubby hands are raised to either side of its face. The overall expression of the emoji is one of extreme surprise, shock, or fear. The color of the emoji fades from blue to yellow and back to blue.
